gdt.data.grain

Class Locator

  • java.lang.Object
    • gdt.data.grain.Locator

  • public class Locator
extends java.lang.Object
    Numerous classes within the JEntigrator use a locator as a parameter or a returned value. The locator is a formatted string containing multiple name/value pairs separated by delimiters.
    Since:
    2016-03-11
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Alexander Imas
